"lifeSummary":"Eleanor Towne родилась в 1426 г. в местности троули, кэнт, Англия, Великобритания. Её родителей звали Thomas at Towne и Joane Cheyne. Она вышла замуж за человека по имени Richard Lewknor около 1460 г. в местности постлинг, кэнт, Англия. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын и 1 дочь. Она умерла в 1476 г. в местности постлинг, кэнт, Англия, Великобритания в возрасте 50 лет."},"sm":{"1426–1476":"1426–1476","1416–1446":"1416–1446","1428–Female":"1428–Ua Maliu","1431–Female":"1431–Ua Maliu","1433–1476":"1433–1476","1457–1522":"1457–1522","1460–Male":"1460–Ua Maliu","1380–1430":"1380–1430","–Female":"Ua Maliu","1460":"1460","1380":"1380","1426":"1426","1425":"1425","1457":"1457","1446":"1446","1522":"1522","1433":"1433","1476":"1476","1431":"1431","1430":"1430","about 1476":"e tusa o le 1476","about 1430":"e tusa o le 1430","about 1460":"e tusa o le 1460","1428":"1428","1416":"1416","Throwley, Kent, England":"Throwley, Kent, Egelani","Postling, Kent, England":"Postling, Kent, Egelani","Postling, Shepway, Kent, England":"Postling, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","Challock, Ashford, Kent, England":"Challock, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","St Michael & All Angels Church, Faversham, Kent, England":"Faversham, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","Sussex, England":"Sussex, Egelani","Towne Place, Throwley, Faversham, Kent, England":"Throwley, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom"},"sk":{"1426–1476":"1426–1476","1416–1446":"1416–1446","1428–Female":"1428–Zosnulá","1431–Female":"1431–Zosnulá","1433–1476":"1433–1476","1457–1522":"1457–1522","1460–Male":"1460–Zosnulý","1380–1430":"1380–1430","–Female":"Zosnulá","1460":"1460","1380":"1380","1426":"1426","1425":"1425","1457":"1457","1446":"1446","1522":"1522","1433":"1433","1476":"1476","1431":"1431","1430":"1430","about 1476":"okolo 1476","about 1430":"okolo 1430","about 1460":"okolo 1460","1428":"1428","1416":"1416","Throwley, Kent, England":"Throwley, Kent, England","Postling, Kent, England":"Postling, Kent, England","Postling, Shepw